@startuml SD-04
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #888888
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #444444
skinparam sequenceParticipantFontSize 12
skinparam sequenceMessageFontSize 11

title SD-04: Sapaan & Percakapan Umum (Greeting)

actor "Pengunjung\n(Browser)" as User #4A90D9
participant "Laravel\n(ChatbotController)" as Laravel #2E8B57
participant "ChatbotService\n(Laravel)" as Service #50C878
participant "Flask\n(app.py)" as Flask #E67E22
participant "ChatbotEngine\n(engine.py)" as Engine #8E44AD

== 1. User Kirim Sapaan ==
User -> Laravel : POST /chat\n{message: "halo, selamat pagi"}
activate Laravel
Laravel -> Service : predict("halo, selamat pagi")
activate Service
Service -> Flask : POST /predict\n{message: "halo, selamat pagi"}
activate Flask

== 2. Deteksi Intent Sapaan ==
Flask -> Engine : process("halo, selamat pagi")
activate Engine
note right of Engine
  Clean text → "halo selamat pagi"
  predict_intent() → SVM classifier
  Intent terdeteksi: "sapaan"
end note

Engine --> Flask : intent = "sapaan"
deactivate Engine

== 3. Buat Respons Sapaan ==
note right of Flask
  Cek waktu saat ini:
  04:00-11:00 → "Selamat pagi"
  11:00-15:00 → "Selamat siang"
  15:00-18:00 → "Selamat sore"
  18:00-24:00 → "Selamat malam"
end note

Flask --> Service : {intent: "sapaan",\nresponse: "Selamat pagi! Ada yang bisa saya bantu?\nSilakan tanya lokasi ruangan yang Anda cari.",\nmatch_score: 1.0, best_room_id: null}
deactivate Flask

== 4. Tidak Ada Ruangan (Greeting Only) ==
note over Service
  best_room_id = null
  → rooms = [] (kosong)
  → options = null
end note

Service --> Laravel : {message: "Selamat pagi!...", rooms: [], intent: "sapaan"}
deactivate Service

== 5. Tampilkan Respons ==
Laravel --> User : JSON {message, rooms: [], intent: "sapaan"}
deactivate Laravel

note over User
  Browser tampilkan pesan chatbot:
  "Selamat pagi! Ada yang bisa saya bantu?"
  (Tanpa card ruangan)
end note

@enduml
